Why is there matter-antimatter asymmetry? Sakharov in 1967 found that violation of three symmetries could cause it if all of them occured:

* charge congregation symmetry
* time reversal symmetry
* thermal equillibrium

There are no satisfactory models that fulfill these conditions.

